	<div class="newsbody">
<p class="">Dear MUHSD Families,</p>
<p class="">With the recent news and concern regarding the coronavirus or COVID-19, I wanted to keep you updated on what we are doing as a district.</p>
<p class="">Please take a moment to read <a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_241806/site_241807/Documents/Coronavirus-Letter-to-Parents.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank" class="">Superintendent Mike Westcott's letter regarding the coronavirus</a>Â in its entirety.</p>
